{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks/task-93","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Govoriti/reći <span class=\"highlighted-text\">promote</span> je pomoći, podstaći ili pomoći nečemu da raste ili uspe.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Ethics</span> Ovo su važni moralni kanoni koji pomažu ljudima da odluče šta je ispravno.</p>\n<p>Pamoja, kusema <span class=\"highlighted-text\">promote ethics</span> znači podsticanje dobrog i pouzdanog ponašanja na radnom mestu. Na primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Companies promote ethics to ensure fairness and honesty among employees.</span> - To znači da kompanije podstiču dobro i pouzdano ponašanje kako bi zaposleni postupali pravedno.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks/task-93"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Šta znači reći <span class=\"highlighted-text\">promote ethics</span> na poslu?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Podsticanje dobrih i pouzdanih navika.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Zaraditi više novca.</p>","feedback":"<p>Promovisanje vrednosti je o etičkom ponašanju, a ne o zaradi novca.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Organizovati proslavu.</p>","feedback":"<p>Podizanje vrednosti je u pitanju etičkih principa, a ne organizovanje događaja.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Takmiči se sa drugima.</p>","feedback":"<p>Radi se o razvijanju dobrih vrednosti, a ne o takmičenju.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":1}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"interview-room2.png","characters":[{"character":"James","position":{"x":50,"y":15,